reviewText: the ultimate form for this epic Sun Ra Arkestra work - fully detailed articles and breathtaking photos - miss and weep...

This is by far the best packaging of this film ever.....with new commentary by producer Jim Newman
you get a great book and the soundtrack on CD too !!
.....look no further this is the one to get !!  The book has a Forward by Wayne Coyne of The Flaming Lips.
you won't be disappointed.
